</div></div><div class="mods-column-ll"><div class="whitebox"><h2>BEGINNING TURFSIDE</h2>After you've read our <a href="http://fav.me/dbj86wg">Code of Conduct</a>,&nbsp;<a href="http://fav.me/dbj50mk">How to Join</a>, and officially joined TS, you will be gifted 50,000c and one stall.&nbsp;Once you see your Username in the Spreadsheet (Banking&gt;"The Vault"), you can begin playing. 

While you are welcome to jump right in, there are a few thing you should know first! Don't let the length of the journal scare you, Turfside is very intuitive once you've gotten started. Please read this guide and the linked information carefully, and if you have any questions&nbsp; feel free to ask in the Discord server! We'd be happy to help!</div></div></div>
<h1>CURRENCY SYSTEM and REFERRALS</h1><div class="whitebox">You may have noticed when you joined, you were gifted 50,000c!&nbsp;This fictional currency, known as "Coins", is the only form of currency approved for essential group elements (horses, slots, items, etc). <b>You may NOT sell or buy horses/slots/etc for dA points, real currency, or any other form of fictional currency</b>. However, extra elements that don't impact game-play, such as Stable Maps, YHHs, Commissions, etc., may be bought with any type of currency, coins or otherwise. This is to maintain fairness and balancing of item rarities.&nbsp;&nbsp;A player's up-to-date coin balance is recorded in The Vault.&nbsp;You can earn coins by racing your horses, offering horses up for breedings, selling horses and unused items, and so on. 

<h3>Referral System</h3>Each time a player lists you as their referrer upon joining, you'll earn Coins (10,000c). Additionally, advertising Turfside in a Poll, Journal, or comment (whether in discord or dA) will earn you 5,000c. This can be done <b>once per month</b>, you must note the group to redeem these Coins. A requirement for the journal, poll, or comment, is that you must mention a feature or function of Turfside you like the most.

</div><div align="center"><small><a href="https://sta.sh/01x1msyutfnh#top">Back to Top</a></small></div>

<h1>PLAYER LIMITS and REFRESH</h1><div class="whitebox">Turfside runs on a weekly schedule. Each player is limited in the number of Trainings, Races and Leases they can do each week. The exact maximum limit depends on the type of Trainer hired, the type of Jockey hired, and the player's PR Bonuses. Once you have reached your weekly limit, you will be unable to submit more until the "refresh". Each week, this <b>refresh occurs on Sunday at 11:59 PM CST</b> regardless of your own timezone and every player's limits are reset so they can begin submitting again. A countdown can be found on :devturfside:'s homepage on the right side. You can view your limit in <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1AIb4O65weeV30oBOP2cxirGvvUuXH2HwBlPkBn3Nqws/edit?usp=sharing">The Vault</a>.</div><div align="center"><small><a href="https://sta.sh/01x1msyutfnh#top">Back to Top</a></small></div>

<h1>TRAINER INFORMATION</h1><div class="whitebox">In Turfside, horses have <b>5 different stats</b> (Speed, Stamina, Breaking, Power, Courage) that helps determine how successful they'll be in races. In order to increase a horse's stats, you must first<a href="https://www.deviantart.com/comments/1/798609698/4735584820"> hire a Trainer</a>. Once hired, the fee will be deducted from your Coin Balance and the Trainer will work for you for one IRL month. Your trainer's "expiration date" will be listed in The Vault under column "TED".&nbsp; Your "TU" shows how many trainings you have available.</div><div class="hh"><div class="ll"><div class="purplebox">There are four different Trainers types, the more expensive, the more you can train your own horses and lease others' horses!</div>
<div class="divTableBody"><div class="divTableRow">
<div class="divTableHead"><h4>TYPE</h4></div>
<div class="divTableHead"><h4>FEE</h4></div>
<div class="divTableHead"><h4>BENEFITS</h4></div>
</div><div class="divTableRow">
<div class="divTableCell">Rookie Trainer</div>
<div class="divTableCell">6,000c / 1 month</div>
<div class="divTableCell">Train horses 20x Week
Lease others' 20x Week</div></div><div class="divTableRow">
<div class="divTableCell">Rising Star Trainer</div>
<div class="divTableCell">12,000c / 1 month</div>
