Lease others' 80x Week
</div></div></div><div class="rr"><div class="whitebox">&nbsp;When a trainer's contract expires, you may choose to rehire them or select a different trainer type. You may also fire a trainer before the one month is finished.&nbsp;</div><div class="whitebox">If you previously had a Rookie Trainer hired, and you fire him and hire an All-Star Trainer, your weekly Training and Leasing limits will jump from 20 to 50 the moment the trainer is hired. 

This is the same when downgrading Trainers. If you had an All-Star Trainer hired, and you fire him to hire a Rookie Trainer, your training and leasing limit drops immediately from 50 to 20. <b>If this causes you to be over your limit</b>, then you won't be able to train until the refresh and your TU is reset back down to 0.</div></div>
<div class="clear"></div><div align="center"><small><a href="https://sta.sh/01x1msyutfnh#top">Back to Top</a></small></div>
