<h1>GUIDE TO THE TURFSIDE SPREADSHEET</h1><div class="whitebox">In Turfside, we use Google Spreadsheets to keep track of players and their horses. You can check it at any time to get updated information about your horses, money, inventory and more. If you are not familiar with Sheets, that's okay! The following is an explanation of what all the boxes are for, per tab.</div><div class="mods-hh split-70"><div class="mods-column-ll">
